
Usage:
  1) Run ray simulation. E.g.:
    /home/l.martire/TMP/GeoAc/GeoAc3D -prop AMGeoAc.met z_src=12 theta_step=5 theta_min=-90 theta_max=-10 bounces=1 azimuth=160 freq=3
  
  2) Plot resulting rays:
    python ./plot_utils/plotResults.py -f ./AMGeoAc_raypaths.dat
  
  *) Look at GeoAc's manual:
    /home/l.martire/TMP/GeoAc/GeoAc3D
  
  *) Look at plotResults.py's manual:
    python ./plot_utils/plotResults.py -h
